org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.protocolPB

Interface ReconfigurationProtocolPB

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.protocol.proto.ReconfigurationProtocolProtos.ReconfigurationProtocolService.BlockingInterface

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Evolving
public interface ReconfigurationProtocolPB
extends org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.protocol.proto.ReconfigurationProtocolProtos.ReconfigurationProtocolService.BlockingInterface
    Protocol that clients use to communicate with the NN/DN to do reconfiguration on the fly. Note: This extends the protocolbuffer service based interface to add annotations required for security.
